title: 820-3332 battery not recognized on OS
message:
Any fault history available?
Turns on with both charger and battery connected?

Post exact PPBUS_G3H voltage w/ and w/o battery connected.
Check voltage and diode mode to ground on SCL/SDA lines of battery bus.
